OL,3,CUK business confidence plunges to
OL,4,Clowest level on record
OL,6,FBusiness confidence slumped to its
OL,7,Flowest level on record last month amid
OL,8,Fconcerns over soaring costs, according
OL,9,Fto a new survey of company bosses.
OL,11,FData from the Institute of Directors
OL,12,F(IoD) showed that firms said higher
OL,13,Flabour costs has been the biggest
OL,14,Fcontributor to growing pessimism about
OL,15,Fthe economy.
OL,17,FThe industry group's monthly economic
OL,18,Fconfidence index, which measures
OL,19,Fbusiness leader optimism about the
OL,20,Fprospects of the UK economy, posted a
OL,21,Fminus 74 reading for September.
