OL,3,CUK business confidence plunges to
OL,4,Clowest level on record
OL,6,FIt marked a significant decline from
OL,7,Fminus 61 and struck the lowest level
OL,8,Fsince the index was launched more than
OL,9,Fnine years ago.
OL,11,FThe previous record low was a reading
OL,12,Fof minus 72 recorded in July this year
OL,13,Fin the face of worries over trade
OL,14,Ftensions.
OL,16,FIn the fresh research, business bosses
OL,17,Falso saw cost expectations increase to
OL,18,Freading of plus 89 amid an uptick in
OL,19,Finflation.
