OL,3,CUK business confidence plunges to
OL,4,Clowest level on record
OL,6,FAround 83% of surveyed leaders linked
OL,7,Fthe worsening outlook to higher labour
OL,8,Fcosts, while supply chain inflation
OL,9,Fand energy costs were also highlighted
OL,10,Fas significant factors.
OL,12,FLabour costs jumped for many firms
OL,13,Ffrom April after the Government
OL,14,Fincreased the national minimum wage
OL,15,Fand National Insurance Contributions
OL,16,F(NICs) for businesses.
