OL,3,CUK business confidence plunges to
OL,4,Clowest level on record
OL,6,FAnna Leach, chief economist at the
OL,7,FIoD, said: "Business confidence has
OL,8,Fplumbed new depths in September,
OL,9,Ffollowing a fleeting improvement at
OL,10,Fthe tag-end of summer.
OL,12,F"Conditions worsened across the board,
OL,13,Fwith cost expectations hitting a
OL,14,Frecord high, driven notably by
OL,15,Femployment costs. Investment
OL,16,Fexpectations declined again, although
OL,17,Fremained somewhat above the most
OL,18,Frecent low in November 2024.
