OL,3,CUK business confidence plunges to
OL,4,Clowest level on record
OL,6,F"Meanwhile headcount expectations
OL,7,Fcontinue to seesaw as the effects of
OL,8,Fthe April rises in employment taxes
OL,9,Fand the living wage, alongside future
OL,10,Fconcerns over employment regulations,
OL,11,Fcontinue to reverberate across
OL,12,Fcompanies."
OL,14,FShadow chancellor Sir Mel Stride said:
OL,15,F"Business confidence has been
OL,16,Fshattered, not by global uncertainty,
OL,17,Fbut by deliberate choices made by the
OL,18,FLabour government."
